snippet.title: Woodsy Whatnots - Paperverse Direct 2024 First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2824720/Woodsy_Whatnots/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/WoodsyWhatnots

Made in collaboration with the Paperverse 2024 Direct.

Woodsy Whatnots is a solo developed 2.5D RPG by Josh McLean ("Chiptroid"). Inspired by papery classics, you explore a rich world of wacky fantasy species, and spin-smash your way through even wackier foes!
